It showcases two flannel shirts with a plaid design, one displayed on the left and the other worn by a model on the right. The price range is listed as 109,000 to 199,000 VND, with a discount noted. The product has a high rating of 4.8 out of 5 from 41 reviews and has been sold 348 times. There are options to add the item to the cart or purchase with a voucher. The interface also includes user profile information and promotional messages.

screens.screen_desc: The screenshot displays a shopping interface for clothing, featuring a flannel shirt. The price is shown as 109,000 VND to 199,000 VND, with a discount from the original prices of 149,000 VND to 239,000 VND, indicating a savings of up to 27%. There are options for different colors and sizes (M, L, XL) available for selection. A quantity selector is also present, along with a confirmation button labeled "Xác nhận" (Confirm). The top of the screen includes user profile information and notifications.

flow_desc: The flow begins with the user requesting to order a product while watching a livestream. Initially, they are presented with a shopping interface displaying various clothing items, including flannel shirts, along with promotional offers. The user taps on the first product image to view details, which showcases product ratings and pricing. Next, they opt to purchase using a voucher and add the item to their cart. Finally, the interface presents color and size options, and the user confirms their selection by clicking the "Confirm" button, completing the product order process seamlessly within the engaging livestream experience.
